{"tid":1610623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"To聽日唔罷/罷不得的手足， 可否幫手做樣嘢？","createTime":"2019-10-01T18:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T19:32:24.000Z","uid":259019,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e775f002f3410b004d308a2ab0a902f8f0e13b8","tid":1610623,"uid":259019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:30:35.000Z","msg":"我明白臨時臨急要罷可能好多人做唔到/唔肯做，但係今日有人比人開槍射中，你哋唔係仲可以當乜事都冇咁樣返工返學呀？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日唔罷工/唔能夠罷工嘅手足，可唔可以今日<span style=\"color: red;\">印一D文宣出嚟</span><br />\n<br />\n中學生嘅將啲文宣擺起自己檯面或者上堂時舉起/棟起<br />\n<br />\n大專/大學生上堂舉起或者放喺電腦後面show出黎<br />\n<br />\n返工嘅可以放檯頭就放喺檯頭，唔得嘅話就趁冇人注意就貼喺公司當眼處<br />\n<br />\n罷工就話有難度啫～印啲嘢出嚟show出嚟唔難掛～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點都做啲嘢表示吓好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a049c437a74513f106157889ff70b2e45aa536b8","tid":1610623,"uid":259019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:34:39.000Z","msg":"p牌仔推唔到有冇人可以幫手"},{"pid":"1ff6e1f79d61f804dbbe5f8558c26ad9b0ba5795","tid":1610623,"uid":259019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:35:22.000Z","msg":"見到個po嘅幫手推一推可唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3e8e31797393ad67460c5cca61d41c86293d83","tid":1610623,"uid":92488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:36:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a775aa898539a911cfd2a97829cb7e5084f9716","tid":1610623,"uid":259019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:37:57.000Z","msg":"推多幾下得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a879909c0729b6f68afe58a1f6d296bfd6460423","tid":1610623,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:32:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府即將告你暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救義士！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"}]}